,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T15:36:35.000Z","msg":"3隻死臭雞 仲要瞓埋一推 好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T09:28:59.000Z","msg":"你識人？郁啲就話人臭雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T10:34:07.000Z","msg":"識又要同你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46689819038432aa8c25803cfaf4d80adc4f8dc6","tid":730603,"uid":135967,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T10:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的 我叫阿John 讀緊港大法律 今年year2<br />\n雖則我生得咁靚仔 但成日都比朋友恥笑<br />\n原因係我生得似笑波子<br />\n<br />\n「 ya 終於考曬啲科啦」我興奮叫道 <br />\n雖則今日exam 但我前幾日先開始溫 完咗sem 就當然慶祝後才擔心成績 <br />\n<br />\n當我收拾物品 準備回hall打機慶祝時<br />\n「 John ！完咗sem之後 有冇興趣陪靚女我去旅行啊？」中分長髮的女生拍了拍我的肩膀道 <br />\n我側頭一望 露著恥笑表情<br />\n笑道 「 陪靚女就可以 但你係靚女咩？」<br />\n她面帶微笑 大力扭著我的耳仔道「 想死咪出聲....」<br />\n我連忙解釋「 講笑咋 講笑咋」<br />\n<br />\n介紹翻 佢叫姚中南 阿May <br />\n係我中同 中學三年同班 咁啱一齊入同一間U又同一科<br />\n萬年不變的中分頭 係我長期恥笑既目標<br />\n雖然她的樣貌不錯 但身材勉強有B  而且成日同我鬥串<br />\n似足男人婆 所以我覺得佢個名 姚中南 改得一啲都冇錯<br />\n中分頭加男人婆 中男 中男<br />\n<br />\n「 咁你去唔去阿 你去我預埋你啦 」May沒好氣道<br />\n「 中南你想去邊先 澳門？深圳？長洲？」私底下我鍾意叫佢中文名<br />\nMay露出仇視的目光 不屑的眼神令我感到有點尷尬<br />\n她道「 台灣 或者 韓國 我地想近近地 又唔洗用太多錢」<br />\n「 你地...？仲有邊個？」<br />\n<br />\n「嘿！梗係我兩個好姐妹 shandy 同 Ada！」阿May翹起雙手 挺起嬌小的胸脯 令我不禁呆望了半刻<br />\n「 咁細...」我心想 但想法衝口而出<br />\n「 咩啊 你up乜」May不明所以地望著我 終於發現我的目光停留在自己身上 連忙拍打我<br />\n「 喂啊！」<br />\n被識穿的我只好轉移視線 到處張望<br />\n「 唔係 我話咁...少..人姐 3嗰女仔 我係度會晤會晤係咁方便啊？」<br />\n「 我見你放假成日係留係屋企打機 先問下你去唔去咋 識咗你咁耐 我信得過你wo 最多咪我同你同一間房咯...」May越講越細聲 搞到我聽不到最後一句<br />\n有得同靚女去旅行 或者可以為我既sem break帶來色彩「 好啊 我跟埋去啊」<br />\n「 一陣黎我間房搵我 我約咗佢地食dinner 順便介紹佢地比你識啊 你記得我邊間室啦」May罕有地露出微笑說道 然後轉身離去<br />\n<br />\n「 okok 一陣見 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cdce63bd0d1a5577ca06e8ecbb617433fca4cb7","tid":730603,"uid":135967,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T10:56:05.000Z","msg":"諗咗嗰大概故仔方向 應該寫到嗰短篇 大約10幾章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 重甜定少甜 唔👌睇我就收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decddaf8f117b982ec7095f9811c06baccadfc8e","tid":730603,"uid":69836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"中分係咪即係攬住條仔隻腳個條女?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 磨牙"},{"pid":"44dd58f06025872f520e6b6aee10f584537ccb1d","tid":730603,"uid":69836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cdce63bd0d1a5577ca06e8ecbb617433fca4cb7","tid":730603,"uid":135967,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T10:56:05.000Z","msg":"諗咗嗰大概故仔方向 應該寫到嗰短篇 大約10幾章<img src=\"/asset