":730603,"uid":135967,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「 你得未啊？搞咁耐都未得既」我不耐煩地敲著門道<br />\n話口未完 門瞬間被拉開 露出狹窄的門縫 令人想窺探門後既環境<br />\n<br />\n阿May 雙手扶著門 身高167的她露出上半身 抬頭望著我<br />\n［利申 我176］<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近距離看到她長長翹起的眼睫毛 深深的黑眼圈 頭髮亂糟糟 像剛起床的樣子<br />\n<br />\n「 嘿嘿...頭先考完試我翻上黎就攤係床玩手機 攤下攤下就訓著咗啦 阿呵... 」懶洋洋的聲音伴隨濃烈的起床氣<br />\n<br />\n「 哇屌你 刷牙換衫啦！ 你又話約咗佢地dinner..」我推開門 像不請自來地走進室內<br />\n<br />\n「 哇！」阿May慢半拍 來不及阻止我 我已經看見房內亂掛的內衣褲 而且只穿內褲的她...<br />\n出生這麼久 我還是第一次看見異性只穿內衣的樣子<br />\n這刻像經過很久 如果我腦有截圖功能cap底就好<br />\n May瞬間滿臉通紅 然後9秒9用手遮住 我都即刻合埋對眼 轉身背著她<br />\n<br />\n我強裝鎮定地說道「 呃..我家姐平時係屋企都係咁樣 我睇慣曬ga啦 」<br />\n我生硬地轉移話題「 你快啲換衫 執好個人我地行啦」<br />\n「 哦 」的一聲後 阿May全程都一言不發<br />\n<br />\n就這樣尷尬地過了10分鐘 我們肩並肩走向電梯<br />\n阿May紅都面曬咁問我「 你睇到曬？ 」<br />\n我迴避她的眼神 微微點頭<br />\nMay低頭沈默咗半刻「 我約咗佢地去旺角打邊爐 」<br />\n「 我好善忘 不過唔可以 再.有.下.次.」阿May細聲道 <br />\n「 好的... 」<br />\n她想我忘記剛才的事情 不再提起嗎..好吧 <br />\n<br />\n一個車程 讓尷尬的氣氛緩和不少 終於來到旺角某XX廣場<br />\n「 May...頭先WhatsApp你做咩唔應我地阿」一個七三分界女神頭的女生走過來說道<br />\n聽上來聲音很溫柔 是May的熟人嗎 那麼.....<br />\n<br />\n「 有咩...阿！sorry啊 我手機漏咗係hall啊 」May摸了摸空空的褲袋 心不在焉地回道 還不經意地看了我一眼<br />\n她用手臂撞了撞我的腹部 像提示我什麼<br />\n<br />\n我黑人問號地看著她<br />\n「 唉 真係蠢人冇藥醫 」May說罷便走向女生身旁 <br />\n<br />\n「 我叫林 山 地... 」女生尷尬地吐出名字<br />\n「 噢！原來May想我自介 點解我蠢到get唔到？」我心想<br />\n等等 這女生的名字怎麼這麼奇怪...山地！？莫非就是剛才提及過的shandy？ <br />\n想到這點 我不禁開始我的賤人mode 她的英文名是 Shandy Lam嗎？林山地？<br />\n<br />\n我強忍笑容 一臉正經地說「 hi 我叫John 係阿May既朋友」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81671b785efaf3965c4b06a9cee027d0f0ef2bfc","tid":730603,"uid":135967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:49:18.000Z","msg":"大力一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4f29e127a463c7676baf2d627b1de062e35ef7","tid":730603,"uid":135967,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"48d41a7cf6b678c0b6763aa95c20aacf54a6e884","tid":730603,"uid":69836,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T11:42:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:51:46.000Z","msg":"原來中分頭條女咁矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇155<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5d0779b65d1196f3f0a301edfd8a475ff1cc5a","tid":730603,"uid":135967,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T13:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「 我叫John 」我主動伸出友誼之手<br />\n林山地都主動行過來和我握了握手<br />\n<br />\n「 你叫我Shandy得啦 唔好叫我中文名 好奇怪」Shandy怕怕醜醜咁連忙矯正叫法<br />\n我望了望 Shandy都幾高 穿了個厚墊鞋後 身高直逼176的我 <br />\n穿著白色背心熱褲的她 凸顯出姣好身材 但性格卻與身材不符 雖然身材十分火辣 但性格卻十分慢熱 內向 正所謂表裡不一？<br />\n見了第一眼後 我的視線便無法離開Shandy 她無可挑剔的身材比例 瘦長白滑雙腿 與旁邊一樣等候入座的港女截然不同 蒼白的膚色 楚楚可憐的雙眼令人有想保護的錯覺<br />\n<br />\n因為仲有一個人未到 所以我地係火鍋店外一邊聊天一邊等待 <br />\n「 咦 Shandy你係咪唔太運動ga? 」我抱有好感地打開話題<br />\n「 你又知既...我成日病ga 份人又弱啲 所以我偏向做啲文靜啲既...冇啦啦做咩咁問既？」Shandy瞧了瞧我 很快便轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n「 哈哈 我見到你咁皮膚咁好咁白 對比到隔離...黃黃地..好奇問下姐」我抱頭笑道<br />\nShandy笑道「 John唔好咁衰啦」<br />\nMay過了一會兒才理解到我的言外之意<br />\n「 你話邊個黃黃地阿！ 你就黃阿 我不知幾白！燈光問題咋！」就在May發狂大鬧的時候 Ada終於到了<br />\n「 Sorry 遲咗小小 咦 晤係我地三個咋咩」Ada不明地看著我<br />\n「 Shandy！ Ada ！我地三個食 我唔識佢ga！」説罷便拉著她們進去<br />\n<br />\n「 Hello 原來你就係John～」Ada帶有餘音地說<br />\nAda的五官也很端正 雖然沒有Shandy那麼女神<br />\n但已經很漂亮 加上薄薄的瀏海 性格隨和主動 應該不缺追求者<br />\n「 係啊 我就係John～你係Ada～？」我學Ada的語氣回答<br />\nAda被我的舉動引笑 連忙揮手道「嘻嘻 阿May以前提起過你 你真係幾有趣 」並向我單了單眼<br />\n「 Ada笑點好低ga你唔好引佢笑 如果唔係 佢會笑到停唔到」阿May阻止我繼續講<br />\n<br />\n接著我們傾了一輪旅行的細節 最終決定到泰國<br />\n原因是我堅持夏天的季節當然去游水嬉戲 <br />\n而且台灣和韓國 Ada與Shandy已經去過 <br />\n<br />\n整個行程也很衝忙 過了不久<br />\n終於來到出發的第一天<br />\n「 死啦 我冇帶藥！」Shandy在機場檢查行李時驚叫<br />\n「 我有！肚痛頭痛胃痛乜都齊！」我拿出一早收拾好的醫療包<br />\n「 好重啊..」身形嬌小的May推著有她半個身高的行李車說道<br />\n我一言不發便輕輕換轉她的手 由我來推行李車<br />\n完成了登記手續 影相之後 很快便上機坐著<br />\n座位是<br />\n<br />\n無聊的我問Ada一個問題「 Ada 」<br />\n「 咩？ 」Ada打側頭看著我 飛機狹窄的座位 拉近我們彼此的距離 肩膀碰著肩膀 不禁令我們有點面紅尷尬<br />\n今天的她穿著碎花連身裙 不知道是不是女生們的喜好 要求所有人有度假氣氛的衣著 也是我第一次在機場穿著沙灘褲<br />\n<br />\n「 你知唔知呢 點解飛機飛咁高....但係點都撞唔到啲星星既？」我慢慢問道 懶有幽默 相信笑點極低的她絕對無法忍受<br />\n「 呃...嘻..唔知wo 開估開估」不出我所料 Ada已經被我on9的語氣引起笑容<br />\n<br />\n「 因為...」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd106bf4f3ec85bbc0dfa8d850c652d3a853a741","tid":730603,"uid":60555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T14:03:19.000Z","msg":"求佢地ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469f25e38d75ad5d990ff2d347b99736da71df70","tid":730603,"uid":130308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T00:05:29.000Z","msg":"勾起傷心回憶<br />\n又係一男三女 同男友加埋我兩個fd去<br />\n大家都識嘅<br />\n最後佢鍾意左我個fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aaaf4e63742f9d750c741431f33a9cf37d812c2","tid":730603,"uid":135967,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T02:33:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d28b67abc9c77a0eeccf317952198752dd03255","tid":730603,"uid":153051,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aaaf4e63742f9d750c741431f33a9cf37d812c2","tid":730603,"uid":135967,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T02:33:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/120744_e76429be71274df19e6196655d1f34e3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F120744_e76429be71274df19e6196655d1f34e3.png&h=f516c630&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"921afb93408063fcbf63fb36ef7ac7c3a9400ddd","tid":730603,"uid":69886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:12:22.000Z","msg":"日日係酒店1王3后<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c232035ecce80ecea6e7773bd03b3cb553141e","tid":730603,"uid":135967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:23:18.000Z","msg":"做咩爆曬人地啲嘢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係咪中咗借刀陷阱<br />\n唔敢寫落去"},{"pid":"cc0cbd2b209bb354e41edf378f19ddf90b50f7fe","tid":730603,"uid":60555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"唔好比佢停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c68745735d52c91972a1df4e3ce5e9979f5091","tid":730603,"uid":135967,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「 你知唔知呢 點解飛機飛咁高....但係點都撞唔到啲星星既？」我慢慢問道 懶有幽默 相信笑點極低的她絕對無法忍受<br />\n「 唔知wo 開估開估！！」不出我所料 Ada已經被我on9的語氣引起笑容<br />\n<br />\n「 因為星星識閃咯 咁飛機咪撞唔到」其實個冷笑話都喺聽人地講...我都知好尷尬 不過對付這種女生 用笑話來打開話題是最好不過的方法<br />\n「 仲有冇仲有冇?」Ada瞪大眼睛 用期待熱切的眼神注視我 看來無聊的笑話正正合適<br />\n<br />\n「 um...小明做錯咗事 佢媽咪罰佢跪喺觀音面前 得到寬恕先可以起身 小明跪咗一秒就起咗身 請問點解呢? 」我想了想便道出另一個無聊IQ題<br />\n「 呃...因為觀音娘娘原諒咗佢...? 唔知啊 開估開估!」Ada思考了片刻便要求我說出答案 並把身體轉向我<br />\n「 因為觀音娘娘話 OK 」我作出 OK的手勢<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=i&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiDs5eahY_cAhXB7WEKHQA5CkAQjRx6BAgBEAU&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fonliaolah.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F04%2Fovertvbbob.html&amp;psig=AOvVaw0Eb4zRhjr1R8pkfaSjh5oo&amp;ust=1531123292993875\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Di%26rct%3Dj%26q%3D%26esrc%3Ds%26source%3Dimages%26cd%3D%26cad%3Drja%26uact%3D8%26ved%3D2ahUKEwiDs5eahY_cAhXB7WEKHQA5CkAQjRx6BAgBEAU%26url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fonliaolah.blogspot.com%252F2018%252F04%252Fovertvbbob.html%26psig%3DAOvVaw0Eb4zRhjr1R8pkfaSjh5oo%26ust%3D1531123292993875&h=9fbf65cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n很冷的笑話引來預期的反應 成功博得紅顏一笑<br />\nAda露出彎彎的眼淺和模仿我的手勢 更不經意地露出虎牙 有一半的時間我們都用來聊天<br />\n她開朗的性格和偶爾的接觸 正悄悄地牽著我的心<br />\n<br />\n由於是凌晨機 身旁的May和Shandy早已戴上耳機 深深進入夢鄉<br />\n原本微弱的燈光突然關上 Ada被此舉動嚇到<br />\n我察覺到她微微震了一下 很快便強裝鎮定<br />\n看了她不但笑點低 膽子也很小<br />\n正當我在想如何渡過餘下無聊的時間時 <br />\nAda看著我說「 John 我訓唔著...不如陪我傾陣計 」並用手臂碰了碰我<br />\n「 好啊 反正我都唔想訓」<br />\n「 其實呢 你同阿May有冇野 你中意佢? 」Ada細聲問道<br />\n「  癡線 我當佢朋友咋 話曬我地同中學又咁有緣分 佢咁男仔頭 我先唔會中意佢」此刻的我只想盡快澄清我與May的關係 免得Ada誤會<br />\n「  咁就好 ! 」Ada露出充滿意味的微笑並用手指督了督我的手背 像是寫什麼字<br />\n<br />\n「  喺咩? 我睇唔明wo 不如你講比我知?」我捉著她的手指 故意說道<br />\n她很快便掙脫 同時張開五指 纏著我的手<br />\n我倆的掌心互相印著 像是十字緊扣的模樣 維持了約數秒<br />\n她貼近我的左肩 我能感受到她那柔軟的雙峰在壓著 <br />\n她在我耳邊用喘氣般的語氣說「 唉...估唔..到就..算 ! 訓覺 !」說罷便鬆開我的手 閉上眼睛裝睡<br />\n<br />\n我知道裝睡的人是絕對叫不醒的<br />\n我輕撥Ada的劉海 輕吻了她的臉龐一下<br />\n她立刻張開眼睛 瞪著我扁嘴 道「 你唔驚佢地見到咩 」<br />\n「 我唔記得我做咗啲咩wo 你唔喺訓著咗咩? 」我裝傻問道<br />\n「 ...... 」Ada若有所思地看了看我 便再次閉上眼睛 這次....是真睡了<br />\n<br />\n不知過了多久  飛機到達了目的地<br />\n「 阿!!終於到啦 坐到我腰都痛! 」我伸了個懶腰 便與三位女生走出機場<br />\n迎接我們的是 晴空萬里的藍天<br />\n此刻的我絕對想不到 這此的旅程 會帶來這樣的結果...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿May視覺篇<br />\n<br />\n上咗飛機終於開始六日五夜的泰國之旅!!<br />\n其實我期待咗好耐 你都知啦!返學其實好悶ga嘛 如果可以瘋狂去旅行就好<br />\n我鼓起勇氣叫個衰人陪我去 起初佢都不情不願咁既樣 但見到Shandy同Ada就即刻say yes<br />\n死咸濕佬 我叫就萬般不願<br />\n<br />\n上咗飛機 我都唔知做咩好 飛機張野又硬又逼 點訓到啊<br />\n我叫到Ada同John喺度傾計 我都想傾埋一份<br />\n但聽到John喺咁講埋啲無聊冷笑話 真係聽到我有啲尷尬...<br />\n<br />\n我好似聽日Ada提起我既名 又聽到死人John喺度話我男人婆<br />\n我幾想打佢 正當我準備行動個陣<br />\n我居然見到 John靠近訓著既Ada 錫咗佢一下<br />\n我見到差啲叫咗出聲 佢地應該唔識ga !點解會咁 定喺我睇錯<br />\n<br />\n我感覺心口有啲唔舒服 有種難以形容既難受<br />\nJohn 你唔會喜歡了Ada吧...<br />\nJohn之後都訓著咗<br />\n<br />\n我輕輕把頭靠在他的肩上 希望得到他一絲的溫柔...<br />\n此時John都將頭貼著我的頭頂<br />\n滿腦疑問的我難以入睡<br />\n「其實我都喺想你陪我姐...我唔會將你讓比Ada...」想到這點 我便不自控地伸手捉緊他的手腕 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9d111ecdbd008fb37f5c843787c77df3aed9a1","tid":730603,"uid":135967,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/165444_a60a0570e9817c6c4d7695377cec73ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F165444_a60a0570e9817c6c4d7695377cec73ca.jpg&h=c32db4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nok手勢"},{"pid":"b8f7f2a4588c8ddd28dfe9fda460198de436f1a4","tid":730603,"uid":135967,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"未入戲肉 個post都已經沉到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似寫緊比自己睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57eebf6bdc79558fde858bc083f1a0d5b9e09ab0","tid":730603,"uid":8797,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b8f7f2a4588c8ddd28dfe9fda460198de436f1a4","tid":730603,"uid":135967,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"未入戲肉 個post都